OL,3,CFamilies tell Up Close that system is
OL,4,C'stacked against' those with
OL,5,Cdisabilities
OL,7,FBy Carol Jordan
OL,9,FWhile the focus of our latest Up Close
OL,10,Fcurrent affairs programme was direct
OL,11,Fpayments, I have been
OL,13,Fcontacted by over one hundred families
OL,14,For carers who told me of varying
OL,15,Fissues with the health and social care
OL,16,Fsystem.
