OL,3,CFamilies tell Up Close that system is
OL,4,C'stacked against' those with
OL,5,Cdisabilities
OL,7,FOne consistent theme was the fact that
OL,8,Fthey felt loved ones with
OL,9,Fdisabilities, particularly those who
OL,10,Fare non-verbal, find it more difficult
OL,11,Fto access equitable healthcare that
OL,12,Fable-bodied people receive.
OL,14,FGwyneth McQuiston is responsible for
OL,15,Fthe care package for her 65-year-old
OL,16,Fbrother, Jeffrey, a role he took on
OL,17,Fwhen her mother died 43 years ago.
OL,19,FJeffrey is non-verbal and has learning
OL,20,Fdifficulties.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/13
