OL,3,CFamilies tell Up Close that system is
OL,4,C'stacked against' those with
OL,5,Cdisabilities
OL,7,FIn a matter of fact manner, she says:
OL,8,F"When I went into recovery I said to
OL,9,Fthe girl that he was in for a very
OL,10,Flong time and was he ok.
OL,12,F"She said well he had a palatectomy
OL,13,Fand I said what's that and they said
OL,14,Fthat well his knee cap had been
OL,16,Fremoved... I was absolutely shocked. I
OL,17,Fsuppose then in my naivety I asked
OL,18,Fthem if they gave him a new kneecap.
OL,19,FDid they replace it?"
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/13
