OL,7,FThe operation left Jeffrey immobile.
OL,8,FIn 2007, the family took a case
OL,9,Fagainst their Trust supported by the
OL,10,FEqualities Commission on the basis
OL,11,Fthat Jeffrey had been discriminated
OL,12,Fagainst because of his disability.
OL,13,FThey won.
OL,15,FJeffrey's cousin Thomas is 10-years-
OL,16,Fold. Like Jeffrey he's non-verbal and
OL,17,Fhas learning difficulties as well as
OL,18,Fbeing on the autism spectrum.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/13
