OL,3,CFamilies tell Up Close that system is
OL,4,C'stacked against' those with
OL,5,Cdisabilities
OL,7,FIn 2020, Thomas's mum, Kirstie, told
OL,8,Fme that he started experiencing
OL,9,Fepisodes. These episodes can be
OL,10,Fviolent. The pictures that she showed
OL,11,Fme are too shocking to publish.
OL,13,FSince then Kirstie says she's been
OL,14,Fbattling to get Thomas the help she
OL,15,Fbelieves he needs... even going to far
OL,16,Fas to pay for a private MRI. The issue
OL,17,Fshe says is that all the symptoms are
OL,18,Fput down to Thomas's existing
OL,19,Fconditions.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/13
