OL,7,FQ: You think he's been treated like a
OL,8,Fsecond class citizen? "I just use that
OL,9,Fexact term all the time."
OL,11,FFor Kirstie and Gwyneth, they say that
OL,12,Fthe constant fight for services is
OL,13,Fexhausting and takes a toll.
OL,15,FGwyneth: "I would dread to think what
OL,16,Fa learning disabled person would be
OL,17,Ftreated like with nobody
OL,19,Fbeside them, and especially if they
OL,20,Fwere non verbal."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/13
