OL,7,FKirstie: "It actually makes me worry
OL,8,Ftoo, because you have to come no
OL,9,Fpeople always tell me not to
OL,11,Fworry about the future ticket day by
OL,12,Fday.
OL,14,F"But you know, like there's so many
OL,15,Fyears between Jeff and Thomas,
OL,16,Fnothing's changed. Is anything going
OL,17,Fto change in the next 20 years for
OL,18,FThomas?
