OL,7,F"I think any parent with a child with
OL,8,Flearning difficulties, if we went
OL,9,Ffirst or something happened to us,
OL,10,Fthat is the biggest fear, even if the
OL,11,Fsystem is fantastic, I'm just hoping
OL,12,Fthat the system is so much better when
OL,13,Fwe're there, because at the minute,
OL,14,Fyes, he's only 11, but we are
OL,15,Fabsolutely petrified of what's beyond
OL,16,Feven the age of 18 for Thomas and no
OL,17,Ffamily should have to feel it's their
OL,18,Ffault."
