OL,7,FA spokesperson for the Western Health
OL,8,Fand Social Care Trust (Western Trust)
OL,9,Fsaid: "We have met with the family to
OL,10,Flisten to their concerns and to agree
OL,11,Fa way forward and will continue to
OL,12,Fkeep in contact with the family as we
OL,13,Fwork to address any issues raised."
OL,15,F"Due to patient confidentiality we are
OL,16,Funable to provide any further detail."
