OL,7,F"Earlier this month, the Department
OL,8,Flaunched 'Equity of Access and
OL,9,FOutcome' following the review of
OL,10,FLearning Disability Nursing in
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,13,F"Work is now underway to develop an
OL,14,Fimplementation plan as part of a wider
OL,15,Fregional service model for those with
OL,16,Flearning disabilities."
